{"tid":1831732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個傻子走左去拍片","createTime":"2020-01-20T15:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T17:05:55.000Z","uid":243060,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4d73e799f393771d04831d25d8baacdd00c53c18","tid":1831732,"uid":243060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"個傻仔就係我朋友，身為終極和理飛，佢除左日日IG文宣，得閒和理玩之外，都真係唔知做到D乜，個傻仔最後走左去整左條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源就咁，咁佢同我傾起1984，好係反烏托邦小說(我都唔知係乜)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁佢就諗住用1984既手法去帶出D政治概念同埋自己既立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過做完唔知點宣傳自己條片，最後搵左我做打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自推十下<br />\n<br />\n睇完覺得好既就支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3_WWBuQUH84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3_WWBuQUH84&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9wKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=2d5951bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3_WWBuQUH84</a>"},{"pid":"4fd3707bc73dfe2ea76fc9b2f350ea2286ebe686","tid":1831732,"uid":243060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"6448601e91c9ab4fe52d77e9e18f95324b129623","tid":1831732,"uid":243060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:13:10.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"76c5c5511be2f5a0843e387ef20bb36fa993151e","tid":1831732,"uid":243060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"6ba4fe29edd4706dc13d44e05602a22395dcf684","tid":1831732,"uid":243060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:13:40.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"77a5669e9642a68